  - knowledge base
abstract: >-
  Open-source multi-LLM chat aggregator: ask web ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini and
  Grok the same question at once through their real web UIs with your own
  accounts, compare answers side by side, merge them into one synthesis, and
  keep everything in VerityDB — a searchable personal knowledge base.
